                <p>Lisa manages sthe business, drawing on her many years of practical experience in fashion & marketing including working as a stylist for Elle and as a fashion buyer for an international retailer.</p>
                <p>She has a BSc in International Fashion Marketing and is a graduate of KLC with a Certificate in Interior Design. Her work focuses on technical hand drawing, lighting design, colour theory & spatial awareness and she has a keen interest in the history of style.</p>
